conkor is a desktop widget utilizing Conky and xdotool.

What makes it unique, is that the widget is interactive
and connects to many sources

Some hot spots are:
* pink/green process names
* weather image (takes to weather URL)
* picture (takes to defined website)
* "News" menu label (takes to online news)
* "Market Watch" (takes to online stock information)
* "Proc" menu label brings up task manager
